items.comment:
[BUG] Fix flaky testLedgerOpenAfterBKCrashed
### Motivation

`BookieFailureTest#testLedgerOpenAfterBKCrashed` is a flaky test case,
it cause some pr failed.

```
Error while recovering ledger
```
